Rarely will your company have this sort of opportunity to move into a new, custom build retail space, specifically designed and build to fulfil your every need.

Building of the modern complex is due to start shortly with completion scheduled 2018.

330 COOPER will be located on Cooper Street, Epping, Victoria within one of the fastest growing residential and business precincts in Melbourne.

330 Cooper is located within the City of Whittlesea. The City of Whittlesea is experiencing unprecedented growth and is now the second fastest growing Municipality in Australia

* 330 Cooper has outstanding exposure to Cooper Street, which carries 50,000 vehicles per day, this will increase to 59,000 vehicles per day by 2021.
* 330 Cooper’s catchment area includes 294,221 people, with a forecast growth rate of a staggering 5% per annum.
* 142,000 people will move to the catchment area in the next 12 years, bringing this population to 435,932 by 2027.
* Large Format Retail (LFR) goods spending generated in the catchment area will grow from $795.4 million in 2014/15 to: $1 billion by 2020/21 and onto $1.24 billion by 2026/27.
* Epping is the designated Principle Activity Centre within the City of Whittlesea.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Display Yard & Huge Main Road Exposure

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to offer, for lease, 370 Cooper Street, Epping. 

The prominent opportunity comprises a modern, purpose built caravan showroom and associated service and detail centre.

Strategically located within the Epping large-format retail precinct, directly opposite the Melbourne Market, the property is located within close proximity to the Pacific Epping Shopping Centre and is just under 500 metres* from the Hume Freeway diamond interchange connecting through to the Metropolitan Ring Road.

Key property attributes include:
+ Total building area: 1,600sqm*
+ Showroom/sales area: 1,200sqm*
+ Pre-delivery & service warehouse area: 400sqm*
+ Clear span temperature controlled showroom
+ Staff amenity and associated offices
+ Multiple on-grade roller shutter doors
+ Excellent on-site parking or dedicated display yard
+ Three (3) phase power

For further information regarding this opportunity or to arrange an inspection of the site, kindly contact CBRE.

CBRE Large Format Retail is pleased to present as the exclusive agents 88 Cooper Street, Epping. The prominent opportunity comprises a modern, purpose built car showroom and associated service and detail centre. Strategically located opposite the Pacific Epping Shopping Centre the property includes a showroom/sales office, a car delivery bay, a service upgrade bay, a service counter/customer lounge/café and associated offices, a spare parts area, a service centre/warehouse area and a mezzanine level training room and amenities.

CBRE are pleased to offer 500 sqm of large format retail space for lease within the established Epping Hub. The dominant retail centre is anchored by national retailers Officeworks, Super cheap Auto and Autobarn and is positioned directly opposite Epping Plaza and in immediate proximity to the Costco site which will be developed in 2017.

The high profile, 60,000sqm corner site is positioned on the junction of High Street and Cooper Street with egress/ingress options via 3 street frontages.

The site also enjoys:
• 4.2 % pa population growth within the immediate catchment
• 37,000 cars passing the site daily
• Opposite regional centre, Pacific Epping SC
• 990 car parks
